variant_descriptions.KORTESTW: Bitwise OR 16 bits masks k1 and k2 and update ZF and CF accordingly.
variant_descriptions.KORTESTB: Bitwise OR 8 bits masks k1 and k2 and update ZF and CF accordingly.
variant_descriptions.KORTESTQ: Bitwise OR 64 bits masks k1 and k2 and update ZF and CF accordingly.
variant_descriptions.KORTESTD: Bitwise OR 32 bits masks k1 and k2 and update ZF and CF accordingly.

op.text:
Performs a bitwise OR between the vector mask register k2, and the vector mask register k1, and sets CF and ZF based on the operation result.

ZF flag is set if both sources are 0x0. CF is set if, after the OR operation is done, the operation result is all 1â€™s.
